{"tid":2507761,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1 票反對《財政預算案》 僅鄭松泰投反對票","createTime":"2021-04-28T08:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T09:26:38.000Z","uid":361987,"like":20,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"3943d0a107efe9d4192ec5e0ffbc571316dfe7aa","tid":2507761,"uid":361987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://external-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQEzxTpaEJJE6OfV&amp;w=500&amp;h=261&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20210428205BRecovered5D-14_30ltn_1200x630cropcenter.png&amp;cfs=1&amp;ext=jpg&amp;ccb=3-5&amp;_nc_hash=AQE4nNWXlzgGGCzy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQEzxTpaEJJE6OfV%26w%3D500%26h%3D261%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcdn.thestandnews.com%252Fmedia%252Fphotos%252Fcache%252F20210428205BRecovered5D-14_30ltn_1200x630cropcenter.png%26cfs%3D1%26ext%3Djpg%26ccb%3D3-5%26_nc_hash%3DAQE4nNWXlzgGGCzy&h=be8d29b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建制派壟斷的立法會，今日（28 日）以 40 票贊成、1 票棄權、1 票反對，極速通過《財政預算案》。民主派撤出議會下，整個財政預算案審議時間，僅用了 2 次會議、共約 8 小時，去年即使主席梁君彥為辯論「劃線」，預算案並開了 5 次會議，審議時間共約 36 小時。<br />\n<br />\n被問到審議時間大幅「縮水」後極速通過、是否有充份辯論？財政司司長陳茂波指議員提出「好多寶貴意見」，不斷互相討論，政府一定會充分考慮議員意見，令措施更貼地切合社會需要，回應市民需求。<br />\n<br />\n有別過去幾年財政預算案成為「拉布」主戰場，今年在民主派撤出議會後，財政預算案的審議亦變成「例行公事」，上星期三審議約 6.5 小時，今午恢復會議後再審議 1 個多小時，在無議員提修正案下極速通過。<br />\n<br />\n僅鄭松泰投反對票<br />\n<br />\n投反對票的是熱血公民鄭松泰，而投棄權的是經民聯的金融服務界議員張華峰。張表示，不滿預算案提出增加股票印花稅，他與業界都不接受，認為這做法會削弱本港作為國際金融中心的競爭力，但政府無考慮業界意見。<br />\n<br />\n對於今次預算案在立法會極速大比數通過，是否審議不足、反映不到社會意見，陳茂波均無正面回應，僅稱會充分考慮議員提出的意見。他又指，預算案推出後社會不同層面有不同反應，但政府會盡量平衡不同界別想法，「但總要有取捨」，會聽取意見後「虛心檢討」。"},{"pid":"979156dba537f42c3e6ff61a387ff539574f2cfe","tid":2507761,"uid":297949,"like":46,"dislike":5,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"真唯一反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做到嘢"},{"pid":"5e27316e1cdf56fc9fb8e05c79d1ab29edf0d99a","tid":2507761,"uid":77196,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"忠誠反對派丫嘛，人大都有呢D存在"},{"pid":"f81f91aa1e0eecf0c6be658a51a7e22ac873ef1c","tid":2507761,"uid":111814,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbSNz7QKMHq1BsNsiVhQoyTFHh7HE8xCob9oiSPHeSeZk?filename=dhopdAe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhopdAe.jpg&h=b93501c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9e0008b6525b8bbe45e721f6af544222728f380","tid":2507761,"uid":134415,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"直接mirror人大投票個display算把啦反正都係投票機器"},{"pid":"5fa7af0f2e0eae17114abfb81845e874e7e3de63","tid":2507761,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e27316e1cdf56fc9fb8e05c79d1ab29edf0d99a","tid":2507761,"uid":77196,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"忠誠反對派丫嘛，人大都有呢D存在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"江澤民同胡錦濤時代就有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/106103475_592364298141440_5289547612872334651_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=eg7LCxlKUDEAX-vnAVX&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=f38de3742825137dc06e5df022c9738e&amp;oe=60AD4F73\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.6435-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F106103475_592364298141440_5289547612872334651_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3Deg7LCxlKUDEAX-vnAVX%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3Df38de3742825137dc06e5df022c9738e%26oe%3D60AD4F73&h=2cc15004&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b43b46e2e98ea0dfe1825fd247035fc5b3cc1c08","tid":2507761,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28